olor: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗战争使 1240 亿美元的海湾汇款生命线面临风险"&gt;明显的迹象表明，经济紧张&lt;/a&gt;，一些工人动用储蓄来维持汇款水平，如果冲突持续下去，可能会导致汇款总额急剧下降。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;最后&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;数千名马拉维移民在德班一座清真寺外的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/8-H0z2lDC-TvHVH5gCeWZ5sY9xv3bK7Y4A-avR52TplBeuBJF3zhUpLsVRjri8Fr99wEHGzyci9g03YtG8ViaaU44vg9qEI7fYn0yypYpvQ99wqQ4BiAJOZ50FCjVymVnBAcgnr4PPuPE719_Wwx-L4PsbOUnUqXTx86ybSORcA4QMg9-jrG5RvruPsJUbacKHeEibqGSre4zbENPRKYzZTIs4V6M0av2tVymGCPP80wg5Q_JOSoJIeD2OQmPxmPercrtJQ6VB5lpUDgCmP-3xuyH944dbWPu0Sio2BCeXcQeHnLFp3zGv4q0cUbGsELy0L5a-UqPwlosogTWskB_huxiG5CUHWrA2H7yS8hoDW1aLi_92OwMdvWSAGEvTFb0DqSwxWP7KH73FxxBwRajuj3qyGOQrMrJ9NkOw6VRxRYo2rYNEl-cKLnEtuY7ya_sQKcwUNzo6Wm90zUX21gATgyhAf6crYVS_t86RlYU9OggA_R71JoUmr-HfCHPamJM0BziBOUsqC_yyA5GkqOJnKHsukRyEYIus7tN2OFt3g/-Xax9EVOF03kqBGH0Nt2OynqMQAt4HGM/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="难民营揭示了南非日益严重的移民危机"&gt;泥泞空地&lt;/a&gt;上寻求庇护，这已成为南非反外国人情绪高涨的最明显表现之一。一个新的治安维持会最初以外国人比当地人受到优惠待遇为由在学校和医院举行抗议活动，现在每天都举行反移民示威活动，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/NugfAX8d0nFYBVdCPsfn0ZH828vBDHq_nw7pepbP59x5rHmLONiwx7_0S9-Q9yWFXd8MWcp_cxAbWjPorZqbJKRijeo26beGqZV6VA2-LTyTWd3I0UGKJsqt_W3LKfu0V8aMeVYrwB_xWdbfJ_ETAWAX3Ijw2v2eySqG7w0hsBFsedSuFGTi-uAm2RUql-NpR_lQA5BYZORaBi3a8oDkCUKIOzIsXQIlVB0Z1RZtcjVmPQOpFttdKKqZ2M-_uTQfKNr5_0iYh2cgqTnwr12kUkr2gP4X8MnvXGYgz-4iPQjKrnz1LcR1Z3obJd5JWJ2CNXW6C_HHqMMCheaLzQpboup_ykdPyJbN9vib5ClEBC3j4yOgyiUJNdsbQNy2uYUByefJrmW2weahwaDRM3x5lIiIh_AR-sa4sOkqKPZt6Jsc-dL8OVEjcFRlZztq7DXqA7yfW8_2O7ot8wWwJjK9_2jAy4yf0G_cybv9hADKqDo4q28VI7k1dnuG57MxaSmkijo5x_PFbxzxMNOZ6UTedNwCIlQ0y4xj8R8oeg/eKroT7kwZhpNlyKSVzcaSuXu-u9ycR2n/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="南非部署警察应对反移民最后期限"&gt;威胁要采取暴力行动，&lt;/a&gt;除非像许多马拉维人一样的无证移民在 6 月 30 日之前离开该国。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQQeyUrC6guc/v0/-1x-1.jpg" alt="TOPSHOT - Hundreds of foreign national queue for food as close to 7,000 of them are instructed to leave the camp at Sherwood Park in Durban on 16 June 2026 and move to Tills Crescent Sports Grounds after fleeing their homes, fearing for their lives amid xenophobic attacks and threats from anti-immigration groups. South Africa has repatriated 2,745 foreigners in the week after President Cyril Ramaphosa vowed tougher action against illegal immigration, the country&amp;amp;#39;s home affairs minister said on Sunday. One of Africa&amp;amp;#39;s largest economies, South Africa has long attracted migrant workers from across the continent, both legally and illegally. But saddled with an unemployment rate above 30 percent, it has experienced recurring spurts of anti-immigrant unrest, including fresh violence in recent weeks. Mobs of South Africans carrying sticks, whips and shields have marched through parts of the country ordering foreigners with no residency papers to leave by June 30. (Photo by RAJESH JANTILAL &amp;amp;#x2F; AFP via Getty Images) Photographer: RAJESH JANTILAL&amp;amp;#x2F;AFP" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="TOPSHOT - 数百名外国人排队领取食物，其中近 7,000 人被指示于 2026 年 6 月 16 日离开德班舍伍德公园的营地，并在逃离家园后搬到蒂尔斯新月运动场，因为他们担心自己的生命受到反移民团体的仇外袭击和威胁。南非内政部长周日表示，总统西里尔·拉马福萨誓言对非法移民采取更严厉的行动后，南非在一周内遣返了 2,745 名外国人。南非是非洲最大的经济体之一，长期以来吸引着来自非洲大陆各地的合法和非法移民工人。但由于失业率超过 30%，该国不断出现反移民骚乱，包括最近几周发生的新暴力事件。携带棍棒、鞭子和盾牌的南非暴徒在该国部分地区游行，命令没有居留证的外国人在 6 月 30 日之前离开。（摄影：RAJESH JANTILAL &amp;amp;#x2F;法新社，盖蒂图片社） 摄影师：RAJESH JANTILAL &amp;amp;#x2F;法新社" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQQeyUrC6guc/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div